&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Tax Compliance and Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;35&quot;&gt;Manage the preparation and filing of federal, state, local, and international tax returns, ensuring accuracy, compliance, and timely submissions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;184&quot;&gt;Oversee multi-state and international tax compliance processes, ensuring adherence to relevant regulations and minimizing risk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;315&quot;&gt;Develop, implement, and maintain tax policies and procedures aligned with company goals and compliance requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
