&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;586&quot;&gt;Ensure accurate tax accruals, reconciliations, and tax-related disclosures in collaboration with the financial reporting team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;716&quot;&gt;Support month-end and year-end close processes, ensuring that tax provisions and related journal entries are accurately reflected.&lt;/p&gt;
